.SH POLICY SYNC
Singine's AI policy workflow is available through the top-level
.B singine policy ai
command family.
The canonical flow is:
.IP "1."
sync a canonical policy pack from LDAP or LDIF sources into a dedicated policy
repository with
.BR "singine policy ai sync" ;
.IP "2."
evaluate Claude or OpenAI/Codex requests against that synced pack with
.BR "singine policy ai evaluate" ;
.IP "3."
persist approvals for governed Collibra paths, repos, or lambda names when a
change is sanctioned with
.BR "singine policy ai approve" .
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
# Sync one canonical policy pack that covers Claude and OpenAI-family systems.
singine policy ai sync \\
  --policy-repo /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine-policy \\
  --ldap-ldif docs/examples/ldap-ai-groups.ldif \\
  --systems claude codex openai-api chatgpt

# Evaluate a Claude read request against the shared policy pack.
singine policy ai evaluate \\
  --policy-repo /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine-policy \\
  --ai-system claude \\
  --environment dev \\
  --network-mode offline \\
  --execution-env local \\
  --operation read \\
  --command-text "rg --files /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine/man" \\
  --path /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine/man/singine.1

# Evaluate an OpenAI/Codex write request using the same synced policy pack.
singine policy ai evaluate \\
  --policy-repo /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine-policy \\
  --ai-system codex \\
  --environment dev \\
  --network-mode offline \\
  --execution-env local \\
  --operation write \\
  --repo-path /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine \\
  --path /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine/man/singine.1 \\
  --lambda-name singine.policy.sync

# Persist approval for a governed Collibra repo or path.
singine policy ai approve \\
  --policy-repo /Users/skh/ws/git/github/sindoc/singine-policy \\
  --ai-system codex \\
  --environment dev \\
  --network-mode lan \\
  --execution-env docker \\
  --operation execute \\
  --command-text "docker compose -f docker/docker-compose.edge.yml up -d --build" \\
  --repo-path /Users/skh/ws/collibra/edge \\
  --resource-grant-kind repo \\
  --granted-by singineer-dev \\
  --reason "Approved Collibra Edge policy sync and validation run"

# Inspect recent governance decisions for Claude and OpenAI/Codex.
singine policy ai report --ai-system claude
singine policy ai report --ai-system codex
.fi
